); 
<bibRefCitation author="Ascher, JS" journalOrPublisher="Zoologica Scripta" pageId="21" pageNumber="34" publicationUrl="http://www.discoverlife.org/mp/20q?guide=Apoidea_species" refId="B3" refString="Ascher, JS, Pickering, J, 2019. . http://www.discoverlife.org/mp/20q?guide=Apoidea_species" url="http://www.discoverlife.org/mp/20q?guide=Apoidea_species" year="2019">Ascher and Pickering 2019</bibRefCitation>
(Israel, as 
<taxonomicName genus="S." lsidName="S. albilabris" pageId="17" pageNumber="30" rank="species" species="albilabris">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="30">S. albilabris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Fabricius)).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="30" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="17" pageNumber="30">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="17" pageNumber="30">*Jordan, Israel, Syria; North Africa, South-Western Europe, Cyprus.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="30" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="17" pageNumber="30">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="17" pageNumber="30">
Mayer (1924) and later 
<bibRefCitation author="Warncke, K" journalOrPublisher="Bericht der Naturforschende Gesellschaft Augsburg" pageId="23" pageNumber="36" pagination="9 - 64" refId="B50" refString="Warncke, K, 1992. Die westpalaearktischen Arten der Bienengattung Sphecodes Latr. . Bericht der Naturforschende Gesellschaft Augsburg 52: 9 - 64" title="Die westpalaearktischen Arten der Bienengattung Sphecodes Latr." volume="52" year="1992">Warncke (1992)</bibRefCitation>
interpreted 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Sphecodes" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sphecodes rubripes" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rubripes">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="30">Sphecodes rubripes</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName genus="S." lsidName="S. albilabris" pageId="17" pageNumber="30" rank="species" species="albilabris">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="17" pageNumber="30">S. albilabris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Fabricius, 1793), but this taxon was restored as a valid species (
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2014-2.RLTS.T47982116A47996274.en" author="Bogusch, P" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="23" pageNumber="36" refId="B22" refString="Bogusch, P, Straka, J, 2014b. . https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2014-2.RLTS.T47982116A47996274.en" url="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2014-2.RLTS.T47982116A47996274.en" year="2014 b">Bogusch and Straka 2014b</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
